name: Dark Gmail by DM
description:
THIS STYLE HAS BEEN DISCONTINUED TO BE UPDATED HERE, PLEASE CHECK MY WEBSITE AND DOWNLOAD THEM FROM THERE:
https://dark-by-dm-website.now.sh/#

More Info: https://dark-by-dm9.webnode.it/
Use the "light" styles in Gmail by going in settings and then themes
Made for the new Gmail UI

If you can't read a mail because of the black background you can turn it to white with this style:
https://userstyles.org/styles/157183/switch-to-white
